	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">Obiit <persName>Bustan</persName> bascia legatis 40m coronatorum pro redimendis, qui capti fuerant ad <persName>Gerbas</persName> propterea, quod aiebat tamdiu pestem Bizantii sęvituram, quamdiu detinerentur.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Miliones septem apud eum reperti cesserunt <persName>Solimano</persName>, et Eli bascia, natione <persName>Sclavus</persName>, ei suffectus est.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Dux <placeName>Sessę</placeName> propediem <placeName ref="l306">Mediolanum</placeName> redibit cum uxore.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la"><persName>Papa Bononiam</persName> cogitat; pro papa erit Puteus cardinalis.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la">Inter nepotes papales non admodum convenit, quum <placeName>Itali</placeName> videant sibi praeferri <placeName ref="l822">Germanos</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la">Agitur de sorore <persName>Philippi</persName> iungenda <placeName ref="l150">Ferrariensi</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la">Subditi a <placeName ref="l1098">Florentino</placeName> exiguntur 300m coronatorum.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la"><persName>Dux Albanus</persName> <placeName ref="l834">Italiam</placeName> repetet cum <persName>Ioanne Austriaco Senarum</persName> principe designando.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la">Munitur <placeName>Bergomum</placeName> vel potius desolatur civibus frustra deprecantibus.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la">Omnia geruntur consilio et autoritate <persName>Sfortie Palavicini</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[Zusätze von <persName ref="p495">Bullingers</persName> Hand:]</note>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de">Es söllend 28 schiff mitt kriegsvolck uß <placeName ref="l875">Hispanua</placeName> zuͦ <placeName ref="l1121">Ianua</placeName> ankummen sin.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de">Die <placeName>3 Länder</placeName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Uri, Schwyz und Unterwalden (vgl. <bibl>SI</bibl> III 1298).</note> schrybend den 3 Pündten, sy söllend die predicanten uß dem <placeName ref="l323">Mousaxer</placeName> taal thuͦn, oder one rächt wöllend sy inen das nitt nachlassen; dann sy in gfar, das ouch die iren anstössen verfürt.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de">Dorumb ist ein tag gen <placeName ref="l98">Chur</placeName> angesähen 28. augusti.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la">Sic isti homines omnibus tandem praescribunt, non tantum <placeName ref="l646">Claronensibus</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="date">[Datum, Unterschrift und Adresse fehlen]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
